8, \"rank\": 0.00382262229689404, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the picturesque streets\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 218}, {\"ngram\": \"fragrant cafes\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 234}, {\"ngram\": \"cyclists\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 254}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators-over15 millionare\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 330}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 364}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's in addition to locals and other French residents traveling to the capital from different parts of the country.\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9961759581455628, \"rank\": 0.00382262229689404, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"locals\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 395}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"different parts\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the uninitiated, Paris can be a lot.\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232593476580693e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recently, the city has grappled with abed bug outbreak, dengue scares, petty crime, public transport workers'strikes, and more.\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"abed bug outbreak\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"dengue scares\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"petty crime\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"public transport workers'strikes\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given the twin popularity of theOlympicsand Paris, surviving (and thriving) in the city can feel like hard work.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232593476580693e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the twin popularity\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 743}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although Paris got a feel for managing big crowds that flocked to Taylor Swift's Eras Tourconcertsearlier this year, the Olympics and Paralympics will have the city buzzing with activity over an extended period.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 778, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232593476580693e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 835, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5626885827127803e-45, \"text\": \"Taylor Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a feel\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"big crowds\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 898}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"activity\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"an extended period\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But fret not-Fortunespoke to tourism, insurance, banking, and culture experts for their tips on navigating the city and having a great experience.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"not-Fortunespoke\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"tourism\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"insurance\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"banking\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"culture experts\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1061}, {\"ngram\": \"their tips\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"a great experience\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like its other big city peers, Paris has an infamous traffic problem.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1163, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232593476580693e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its other big city peers\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"an infamous traffic problem\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the lead-up to the Olympics, several hotspots in the city will be cordoned off, restricting taxi access.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lead-up\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"several hotspots\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1262}, {\"ngram\": \"taxi access\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The biggest pitfall is going to be the traffic.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The biggest pitfall\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"the traffic\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will be very hard to find your way around it, which is why being centrally located at a perfect hotel is the key,\\\" said Jonathan Alder, founder of travel management company Jonathan's Travels.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Alder\", \"score\": 0.6715333953994442, \"rank\": 0.48912921807086734, \"text\": \"Jonathan Alder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Alder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Alder\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your way\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"a perfect hotel\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"the key\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"founder\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1506}, {\"ngram\": \"travel management company Jonathan's Travels\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This level of crowds is going to be a challenge for Paris, specifically when it comes to traffic and crowding.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232593476580693e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This level\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"crowds\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"traffic\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"crowding\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For guests willing to pay for the top hospitality packages, they have created a workaround with a special traffic lane that will only be available to specific vehicles,\\\" Alder toldFortune.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"guests\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"the top hospitality packages\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"a workaround\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"a special traffic lane\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"specific vehicles\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you plan to visit other parts of France before getting to Paris, he cautions against connecting via a major Paris airport-whether Charles de Gaulle Airport or Paris-Orly.\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1895, \"end\": 1901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999974475409378, \"rank\": 2.4789430979854915e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1920, \"end\": 1925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232593476580693e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1970, \"end\": 1975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232593476580693e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1992, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charles de Gaulle Airport\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other parts\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris-Orly\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While cabs (identifiable with a \\\"taxi\\\" sign on their hoods) are very much an option, public transport is still the best way to get around the city.\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cabs\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"taxi\\\" sign\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2079}, {\"ngram\": \"their hoods\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"an option\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2119}, {\"ngram\": \"public transport\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"the best way\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Road and station closures could hamper some routes, sothe RATPandPublic Transport Paris 2024apps will be your friends for real-time updates on what's working and what's not.\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Road and station closures\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2209}, {\"ngram\": \"some routes\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"your friends\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"real-time updates\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, keep your eyes and ears open in case ofany protestsin the areas you are heading to.\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your eyes\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"ears\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"case\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2400}, {\"ngram\": \"ofany\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"the areas\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not forget to leave enough buffer time for delays.\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"enough buffer time\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2489}, {\"ngram\": \"delays\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other safe alternatives include carpooling, renting cycles (aV\\u00e9lib passcould be helpful), and exploring areas by foot.\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other safe alternatives\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"carpooling\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2545}, {\"ngram\": \"renting cycles\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"aV\\u00e9lib\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2569}, {\"ngram\": \"areas\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2612}, {\"ngram\": \"foot\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Uber is offering free ferriesacross the SeineRiver from July 12 to August 3 in addition to taxis.\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Uber\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2627}, {\"ngram\": \"the SeineRiver\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2673}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2683}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2696}, {\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"taxis\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When in Paris, beware of how and where you access your money.\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2730, \"end\": 2735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232593476580693e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your money\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tourists habitually convert local currencies to their home currency to find the best deals in shopping and buying food.\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tourists\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2792}, {\"ngram\": \"local currencies\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2828}, {\"ngram\": \"their home currency\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2851}, {\"ngram\": \"the best deals\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2874}, {\"ngram\": \"shopping\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2886}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The implication?\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The implication\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Exchange rates change daily, even if only by a small percentage, and it costs to use your home currency if you are not careful.\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 3048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Exchange rates\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"a small percentage\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2984}, {\"ngram\": \"your home currency\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Always have some (but not a lot) euros handy and make sure to transact only in euros even when credit card machines prompt you otherwise, London-based fintech firmWise saidin a report about preparing for the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3273, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some (but not a lot) euros\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3088}, {\"ngram\": \"euros\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3134}, {\"ngram\": \"credit card machines\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3165}, {\"ngram\": \"London-based fintech firmWise\", \"from\": 3188, \"to\": 3217}, {\"ngram\": \"a report\", \"from\": 3225, \"to\": 3233}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also warns against resorting to airport or hotel exchanges, which deliberately charge you more.\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"airport or hotel exchanges\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Airports and hotels cater to a captive audience.\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Airports\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3385}, {\"ngram\": \"hotels\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3396}, {\"ngram\": \"a captive audience\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their exchange services will reflect this in their higher fees and poorer rates,\\\" the report said.\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3524, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their exchange services\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3449}, {\"ngram\": \"their higher fees\", \"from\": 3471, \"to\": 3488}, {\"ngram\": \"poorer rates\", \"from\": 3493, \"to\": 3505}, {\"ngram\": \"the report\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other suggested tips include having backup payment options in case your primary card fails and checking if your home bank has any affiliates in France that'll absorb some of the transaction fees.\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3670, \"end\": 3676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999974475409378, \"rank\": 2.4789430979854915e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other suggested tips\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3546}, {\"ngram\": \"backup payment options\", \"from\": 3562, \"to\": 3584}, {\"ngram\": \"case\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3592}, {\"ngram\": \"your primary card\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3610}, {\"ngram\": \"your home bank\", \"from\": 3633, \"to\": 3647}, {\"ngram\": \"any affiliates\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3666}, {\"ngram\": \"the transaction fees\", \"from\": 3700, \"to\": 3720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is another thing people need to be aware of when exploring the streets of Paris-the pickpockets.\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another thing\", \"from\": 3732, \"to\": 3745}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3746, \"to\": 3752}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 3788, \"to\": 3799}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris-the pickpockets\", \"from\": 3803, \"to\": 3824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With more tourists in the city, there may be an increase in petty crime and scams targeting visitors,\\\" said Johannes Thomas, the CEO of German-based travel platform Trivago, citing the example of \\\"the friendship bracelet scam\\\" at attractions like Sacre-Coeur.\", \"from\": 3827, \"to\": 4087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3936, \"end\": 3951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannes_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9999838149115149, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Johannes Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13382576\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannes_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannes_Thomas\"}, {\"begin\": 3993, \"end\": 4000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trivago\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trivago\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trivago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trivago\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more tourists\", \"from\": 3833, \"to\": 3846}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 3858}, {\"ngram\": \"an increase\", \"from\": 3873, \"to\": 3884}, {\"ngram\": \"petty crime\", \"from\": 3888, \"to\": 3899}, {\"ngram\": \"scams\", \"from\": 3904, \"to\": 3909}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 3920, \"to\": 3928}, {\"ngram\": \"the CEO\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 3960}, {\"ngram\": \"the example\", \"from\": 4009, \"to\": 4020}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"the friendship bracelet scam\", \"from\": 4024, \"to\": 4053}, {\"ngram\": \"attractions\", \"from\": 4058, \"to\": 4069}, {\"ngram\": \"Sacre-Coeur\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Avoid flashing any valuables or cash that may draw negative attention.\", \"from\": 4089, \"to\": 4160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any valuables\", \"from\": 4105, \"to\": 4118}, {\"ngram\": \"cash\", \"from\": 4122, \"to\": 4126}, {\"ngram\": \"negative attention\", \"from\": 4141, \"to\": 4159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, avoid street performers or street games, especially [ones] involving money, as this can often be a planned distraction to set up a pickpocket.\\\"\", \"from\": 4161, \"to\": 4318, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"street performers\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4198}, {\"ngram\": \"street games\", \"from\": 4202, \"to\": 4214}, {\"ngram\": \"especially [ones\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4232}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 4244, \"to\": 4249}, {\"ngram\": \"a planned distraction\", \"from\": 4272, \"to\": 4293}, {\"ngram\": \"a pickpocket\", \"from\": 4304, \"to\": 4316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no easy way out with the crowds, no matter where in Paris you go.\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4383, \"end\": 4388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232593476580693e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no easy way\", \"from\": 4331, \"to\": 4342}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 4352, \"to\": 4362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, it's probably best to embrace it, Thomas said.\", \"from\": 4397, \"to\": 4447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4435, \"end\": 4441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"score\": 0.742263585076869, \"rank\": 0.3472103008698539, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Expect overcrowding, long lines and overwhelmed services at popular tourist attractions like the Eiffel Tower, Louvre and other major sites.\", \"from\": 4449, \"to\": 4590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4561, \"end\": 4567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"score\": 0.9993435677891152, \"rank\": 0.0006568633974995785, \"text\": \"Louvre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"overcrowding\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4469}, {\"ngram\": \"long lines\", \"from\": 4471, \"to\": 4481}, {\"ngram\": \"overwhelmed services\", \"from\": 4486, \"to\": 4506}, {\"ngram\": \"popular tourist attractions\", \"from\": 4510, \"to\": 4537}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 4543, \"to\": 4559}, {\"ngram\": \"other major sites\", \"from\": 4572, \"to\": 4589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anticipate increased prices.\", \"from\": 4591, \"to\": 4619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Anticipate\", \"from\": 4591, \"to\": 4601}, {\"ngram\": \"prices\", \"from\": 4612, \"to\": 4618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Accommodation, food and transportation costs tend to spike during major events.\", \"from\": 4620, \"to\": 4699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Accommodation\", \"from\": 4620, \"to\": 4633}, {\"ngram\": \"food and transportation costs\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4664}, {\"ngram\": \"major events\", \"from\": 4686, \"to\": 4698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Visitors may face significantly higher prices, especially for hotels and short-term rentals in central Paris,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 4700, \"to\": 4820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4803, \"end\": 4808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232593476580693e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Visitors\", \"from\": 4700, \"to\": 4708}, {\"ngram\": \"significantly higher prices\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4745}, {\"ngram\": \"hotels\", \"from\": 4762, \"to\": 4768}, {\"ngram\": \"short-term rentals\", \"from\": 4773, \"to\": 4791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Planning trips during peak travel season often brings uncertainties-delays, last-minute cancellations, lost bags, and more.\", \"from\": 4822, \"to\": 4945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Planning trips\", \"from\": 4822, \"to\": 4836}, {\"ngram\": \"peak travel season\", \"from\": 4844, \"to\": 4862}, {\"ngram\": \"uncertainties-delays\", \"from\": 4876, \"to\": 4896}, {\"ngram\": \"last-minute cancellations\", \"from\": 4898, \"to\": 4923}, {\"ngram\": \"bags\", \"from\": 4930, \"to\": 4934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's tricky to prepare for each of these scenarios, but travel insurance can be the key to feeling more in control of your trip.\", \"from\": 4946, \"to\": 5074, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these scenarios\", \"from\": 4981, \"to\": 4996}, {\"ngram\": \"travel insurance\", \"from\": 5002, \"to\": 5018}, {\"ngram\": \"the key\", \"from\": 5026, \"to\": 5033}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 5053, \"to\": 5060}, {\"ngram\": \"your trip\", \"from\": 5064, \"to\": 5073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People could face three types of risks when traveling: financial, medical and travel, Rajeev Shrivastava, founder and CEO of VisitorsCoverage, a travel and health insurance marketplace, toldFortune.\", \"from\": 5076, \"to\": 5274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5162, \"end\": 5168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajiv\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9971726292144434e-17, \"text\": \"Rajeev\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajiv\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajiv\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 5076, \"to\": 5082}, {\"ngram\": \"three types\", \"from\": 5094, \"to\": 5105}, {\"ngram\": \"risks\", \"from\": 5109, \"to\": 5114}, {\"ngram\": \"founder\", \"from\": 5182, \"to\": 5189}, {\"ngram\": \"CEO\", \"from\": 5194, \"to\": 5197}, {\"ngram\": \"VisitorsCoverage\", \"from\": 5201, \"to\": 5217}, {\"ngram\": \"a travel and health insurance marketplace\", \"from\": 5219, \"to\": 5260}, {\"ngram\": \"toldFortune\", \"from\": 5262, \"to\": 5273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People [who] are making these trips have made some heavy investments, including their tickets and the stay,\\\" Shrivastava said.\", \"from\": 5276, \"to\": 5403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these trips\", \"from\": 5301, \"to\": 5312}, {\"ngram\": \"some heavy investments\", \"from\": 5323, \"to\": 5345}, {\"ngram\": \"their tickets\", \"from\": 5357, \"to\": 5370}, {\"ngram\": \"the stay\", \"from\": 5375, \"to\": 5383}, {\"ngram\": \"Shrivastava\", \"from\": 5386, \"to\": 5397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The risks of impromptu cancellations, peak summer heat, and rampant petty crime could become unnecessary stressors in a long-anticipated trip.\", \"from\": 5407, \"to\": 5549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The risks\", \"from\": 5407, \"to\": 5416}, {\"ngram\": \"impromptu cancellations\", \"from\": 5420, \"to\": 5443}, {\"ngram\": \"peak summer heat\", \"from\": 5445, \"to\": 5461}, {\"ngram\": \"rampant petty crime\", \"from\": 5467, \"to\": 5486}, {\"ngram\": \"unnecessary stressors\", \"from\": 5500, \"to\": 5521}, {\"ngram\": \"a long-anticipated trip\", \"from\": 5525, \"to\": 5548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's where travel insurance can help-it lifts the burden off visitors, protecting them in case of unforeseen losses.\", \"from\": 5550, \"to\": 5668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"travel insurance\", \"from\": 5563, \"to\": 5579}, {\"ngram\": \"the burden\", \"from\": 5598, \"to\": 5608}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 5613, \"to\": 5621}, {\"ngram\": \"case\", \"from\": 5642, \"to\": 5646}, {\"ngram\": \"unforeseen losses\", \"from\": 5650, \"to\": 5667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Many insurance policies have coverage for many of these events,\\\" Shrivastava said, adding that insurance is a tool that people consider with varying degrees of seriousness, depending on how much they have traveled.\", \"from\": 5670, \"to\": 5885, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many insurance policies\", \"from\": 5671, \"to\": 5694}, {\"ngram\": \"coverage\", \"from\": 5700, \"to\": 5708}, {\"ngram\": \"these events\", \"from\": 5721, \"to\": 5733}, {\"ngram\": \"Shrivastava\", \"from\": 5736, \"to\": 5747}, {\"ngram\": \"insurance\", \"from\": 5766, \"to\": 5775}, {\"ngram\": \"a tool\", \"from\": 5779, \"to\": 5785}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5791, \"to\": 5797}, {\"ngram\": \"varying degrees\", \"from\": 5812, \"to\": 5827}, {\"ngram\": \"seriousness\", \"from\": 5831, \"to\": 5842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shrivastava says another way to ensure safety is to have emergency contacts who travelers can contact.\", \"from\": 5887, \"to\": 5989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shrivastava\", \"from\": 5887, \"to\": 5898}, {\"ngram\": \"another way\", \"from\": 5904, \"to\": 5915}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 5926, \"to\": 5932}, {\"ngram\": \"emergency contacts\", \"from\": 5944, \"to\": 5962}, {\"ngram\": \"travelers\", \"from\": 5967, \"to\": 5976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let your family remain informed [or] whoever you believe and trust about where you are, where you are traveling to, and what of transportation you are taking,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 5991, \"to\": 6160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your family\", \"from\": 5996, \"to\": 6007}, {\"ngram\": \"whoever\", \"from\": 6029, \"to\": 6036}, {\"ngram\": \"transportation\", \"from\": 6120, \"to\": 6134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruising your way through Paris is not just about getting on the right bus or staying in the right neighborhood.\", \"from\": 6162, \"to\": 6274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6188, \"end\": 6193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232593476580693e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your way\", \"from\": 6171, \"to\": 6179}, {\"ngram\": \"the right bus\", \"from\": 6223, \"to\": 6236}, {\"ngram\": \"the right neighborhood\", \"from\": 6251, \"to\": 6273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's also about taking in some of the culture and blending into the city where you can.\", \"from\": 6275, \"to\": 6362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the culture\", \"from\": 6309, \"to\": 6320}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 6339, \"to\": 6347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noel Wolf, a language teacher and cultural expert at language learning platform Babbel, thinks learning some basic phrases can be a game-changer.\", \"from\": 6363, \"to\": 6508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6363, \"end\": 6367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noel_Gallagher\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.647594501634117e-22, \"text\": \"Noel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noel_Gallagher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noel_Gallagher\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a language teacher\", \"from\": 6374, \"to\": 6392}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural expert\", \"from\": 6397, \"to\": 6412}, {\"ngram\": \"language learning platform Babbel\", \"from\": 6416, \"to\": 6449}, {\"ngram\": \"some basic phrases\", \"from\": 6467, \"to\": 6485}, {\"ngram\": \"a game-changer\", \"from\": 6493, \"to\": 6507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Not only does being able to communicate in the local language facilitate cultural connection, but it is crucial for keeping travelers safe in high-stress, large-scale events such as the Olympics,\\\" Wolf said.\", \"from\": 6512, \"to\": 6720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the local language facilitate cultural connection\", \"from\": 6556, \"to\": 6605}, {\"ngram\": \"travelers\", \"from\": 6637, \"to\": 6646}, {\"ngram\": \"high-stress, large-scale events\", \"from\": 6655, \"to\": 6686}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 6695, \"to\": 6707}, {\"ngram\": \"Wolf\", \"from\": 6710, \"to\": 6714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brushing up on your French will also come in handy when asking for directions or seeking help, making you feel more safe.\", \"from\": 6722, \"to\": 6843, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6742, \"end\": 6748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9961759581455628, \"rank\": 0.00382262229689404, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"directions\", \"from\": 6789, \"to\": 6799}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 6811, \"to\": 6815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People tend to regret not knowing the local language, adding to the stress of travel, Babbel found in a survey.\", \"from\": 6844, \"to\": 6955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6930, \"end\": 6936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babbel\", \"score\": 0.892412517409102, \"rank\": 0.12055801604270001, \"text\": \"Babbel\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babbel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babbel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 6844, \"to\": 6850}, {\"ngram\": \"the local language\", \"from\": 6878, \"to\": 6896}, {\"ngram\": \"the stress\", \"from\": 6908, \"to\": 6918}, {\"ngram\": \"travel\", \"from\": 6922, \"to\": 6928}, {\"ngram\": \"a survey\", \"from\": 6946, \"to\": 6954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Travelerswill also need to familiarize themselves with the geography and public transportation in Paris, so in the event of an emergency or getting separated from their travel partners, attendees can have a general idea of where they are within the city and navigate their way back home,\\\" Wolf said.\", \"from\": 6957, \"to\": 7257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7056, \"end\": 7061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1232593476580693e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Travelerswill\", \"from\": 6958, \"to\": 6971}, {\"ngram\": \"the geography\", \"from\": 7013, \"to\": 7026}, {\"ngram\": \"public transportation\", \"from\": 7031, \"to\": 7052}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 7069, \"to\": 7078}, {\"ngram\": \"an emergency\", \"from\": 7082, \"to\": 7094}, {\"ngram\": \"their travel partners\", \"from\": 7121, \"to\": 7142}, {\"ngram\": \"attendees\", \"from\": 7144, \"to\": 7153}, {\"ngram\": \"a general idea\", \"from\": 7163, \"to\": 7177}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 7203, \"to\": 7211}, {\"ngram\": \"their way\", \"from\": 7225, \"to\": 7234}, {\"ngram\": \"Wolf\", \"from\": 7247, \"to\": 7251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other etiquette tips, such as saying \\\"Bonjour\\\" and keeping a low voice at restaurants, are also helpful to remember.\", \"from\": 7259, \"to\": 7375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other etiquette tips\", \"from\": 7259, \"to\": 7279}, {\"ngram\": \"Bonjour\", \"from\": 7297, \"to\": 7304}, {\"ngram\": \"a low voice\", \"from\": 7318, \"to\": 7329}, {\"ngram\": \"restaurants\", \"from\": 7333, \"to\": 7344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And with that, you should be all set for a Parisian summer.\", \"from\": 7377, \"to\": 7436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Parisian summer\", \"from\": 7418, \"to\": 7435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Safe travels, or as the French would say,bon voyage!\", \"from\": 7437, \"to\": 7489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7461, \"end\": 7467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9961759581455628, \"rank\": 0.00382262229689404, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Safe travels\", \"from\": 7437, \"to\": 7449}, {\"ngram\": \"bon voyage\", \"from\": 7478, \"to\": 7488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2025 Fortune Media IP Limited.\", \"from\": 7495, \"to\": 7527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7502, \"end\": 7509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\", \"score\": 0.9999999293731914, \"rank\": 7.062638512716935e-08, \"text\": \"Fortune\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\"}, {\"begin\": 7516, \"end\": 7518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\", \"score\": 0.9953770129539904, \"rank\": 0.004644450861692918, \"text\": \"IP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00a9\", \"from\": 7495, \"to\": 7496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 7528, \"to\": 7548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Use of this site constitutes acceptance of ourTerms of UseandPrivacy Policy|CA Notice at Collection and Privacy Notice|Do Not Sell/Share My Personal InformationFORTUNE is a trademark of Fortune Media IP Limited, registered in the U.S. and other countries.\", \"from\": 7549, \"to\": 7804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7735, \"end\": 7742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\", \"score\": 0.9999999293731914, \"rank\": 7.062638512716935e-08, \"text\": \"Fortune\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fortuna\"}, {\"begin\": 7749, \"end\": 7751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org